title: examples
pid: 1283148c-24d1-4201-9bbe-7506d1eb3352
body: |2-
  > [('a', 1), ('b', 2), ('c', 3)]
      & partsOf (traversed . _1) %~ reverse
  [('c',1),('b',2),('a',3)]

  > [('a', 1), ('b', 2), ('c', 3)]
  & partsOf (traversed . _2)
  %~ \xs -> (/ sum xs) <$> xs
  [('a',0.16666), ('b',0.33333), ('c',0.5)]
